footnotes: All six datasets contain TripAdvisor restaurant reviews and its associated images as originally curated by Díez et al. [10]. [10].
references: In this work, we apply our proposal to the specific use-case of explaining restaurant recommendations with restaurant images uploaded by users; these datasets were introduced by Díez et al. [10] and contain images of restaurants uploaded in users’ reviews on TripAdvisor in six different cities between 2018-19: Gijón, Barcelona, Madrid, Paris, New York, and London. Table [10] and contain images of restaurants uploaded in users’ reviews on TripAdvisor in six different cities between 2018-19: Gijón, Barcelona, Madrid, Paris, New York, and London. Table I details the number of different users, restaurants and images available in the each dataset; the diversity in population size and geographic location of these cities ensures a comprehensive evaluation. Each example in the datasets is a triad user-restaurant-photo indicating a user uploaded said photograph in their review of a given restaurant.
